@database Speller.guide
@node MAIN
@title "Speller - Improve your spelling NOW! :)"


                   Welcome to the Speller documentation!

  Speller is an educational tool designed to help anyone (who can read
English, of course :}) learn how to spell words.  You can use the default
set of ten words which is very simple, or you can make your own word files
to use in Speller.  Speller consists of three programs, the main program,
the word file generator, and the speech editor.

  Please choose which docmentation you wish to view.

              1.@{"Speller" link spllr} 2.@{"Spelled" link spled} 3.@{"Speeched" link spched}


@endnode
@node spllr
@title "Speller - Lern to spel!"

  Speller is an educational tool designed to help anyone (who can read
English, of course :}) learn how to spell words.  You can use the default
set of ten words which are very simple, or you can make your own word files
to use in Speller.

                               @{"About" link spelabout}
                            @{"Requirements" link spelreq}
